name: XPORT: Address Unknown
description:
XPORT: Address Unknown

Your're an alien working on a space station dock, and your job is to organize packages that come into the dock according to both the available space and shipping requirements.

This was a submission for the Ludum Dare 34 game jam, under the themes of either "growing" or "two button controls".

Developed in Unity.

Most assets by http://kenney.itch.io/
